{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2197d7f00d","title":"给罗元的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7630b0c0fd","index":0,"year":1952,"month":10,"day":22,"articleId":"2197d7f00d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"7816adb640","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"罗元，号翰漠，毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时的历史教员。"},{"id":"698a2dfe2a","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指罗元托李清交给毛泽东的两篇文稿。一篇是罗元鲲的自传，一篇是罗写的《第一师范时代的毛主席》。"},{"id":"f8d6d0b669","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指毛泽东书写的“袁吉六先生之墓”。袁吉六即袁仲谦，是毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时的国文教员，1932年去世。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4eec458f46","type":"title","text":"给罗元鲲的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d"},{"id":"7816adb640","type":"paragraph","text":"翰漠先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d"},{"id":"698a2dfe2a","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十九日赐示敬悉。李先生交来两件以，均已拜读，极为感谢！自传兴会额举，评论深刻，可为后生楷模。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d"},{"id":"f8d6d0b669","type":"paragraph","text":"另件所述“特色”诸点，得之传闻，诸多不实，请勿公表为荷。两件奉还。袁先生基文遵喝书就，烦为转致。新化古寺有所设损，极为不当，此类各地多有，正由政务院统筹保护之法，故不单独写字，尚祈谅之。僧尼老者守寺，少壮从事劳动，此论公允，已转政府有关机关的处。此复。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d"},{"id":"bc0ffad286","type":"subtitle","text":"敬领","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d"},{"id":"fb79f79b7b","type":"paragraph","text":"旅安！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d"},{"id":"119b1c1b1e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d"},{"id":"792a84c318","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年十月廿二日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d"}],"page":{"id":"681d01b8ce","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"2197d7f00d","start":305,"end":305}}}},"__N_SSG":true}